{"tid":1675032,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非入】水魔法師需要你幫手","createTime":"2019-10-25T15:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T15:10:53.000Z","uid":88214,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"6bdd89d69d37840bb55b636eef6cc90772461420","tid":1675032,"uid":88214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">水魔法</span>講就講咗好耐喇<br />\n點解香港仲未成功見到呢個畫面呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1pb3oet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1pb3oet.jpg&h=b270b668&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其實<span style=\"color: blue;\">水魔法</span>一直有人用 但仲有好多進步空間<br />\n不過其實一眾<span style=\"color: blue;\">水魔法師</span>已經好努力進行研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聞說好似已經搵到解決攻擊距離唔夠嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家只差各位和理非幫手 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>帶物資</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ey0WJha.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fey0WJha.png&h=2af2c1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住上面張圖 每人幫手帶幾樣<br />\n大部分都係好易搵 比人搜到都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家叫齊親朋好友一齊帶<br />\n一齊幫班狗狗 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>沖個靚涼</strong></span> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d9e6f9af12094d64958051aac12ba7bb4c8d4f","tid":1675032,"uid":88214,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:10:38.000Z","msg":"For whatsapp老一輩<br />\n「年青人需要你的幫忙🙏🏻<br />\n從今日起每人攜帶少量物資～<br />\n要為他們補給 別再做他們的負累<br />\n同意請分享 請廣傳 好人一世平安❤️」"},{"pid":"1b770a8bce0019b72305757bdce5ac731d70b1aa","tid":1675032,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMvDbNv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMvDbNv.gif&h=fcf15a75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a1e1b0ecba7cdb8e714342b3695840487f445b3","tid":1675032,"uid":88214,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7F0qzj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7F0qzj.jpg&h=ddf574e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港好快會見到㗎喇 大家要幫手推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b511ceffd2aae863fd17989c4f72255ba17711","tid":1675032,"uid":100724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f3f8f7812b848105f67d110585520e7459b9783","tid":1675032,"uid":88214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7d552c64ae85ece228fc5e1b95aeda66ba3ba22c","tid":1675032,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"wwwwwwwwwwwww"},{"pid":"6a95e9cf9096f3feeff2c305608b0b1ad458ad2d","tid":1675032,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6127fea6c326fdea14f0369b084635ded847791c","tid":1675032,"uid":308778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab98e62032fb563aad0497dd085046270934b4d","tid":1675032,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3386adf36a81ffbf44060a068c2a8bd683cfb42","tid":1675032,"uid":88214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"【水魔法實用post】水彈及發射炮台教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1642359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1642359</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9dba7d31aebb98af24429a714caff49403da0